Thread suspension: Unwind register state during x86-64 TLS fast path syscalls

Extend the unwinder to be able to recover untrusted register state for
these syscalls.

 * Add "End" labels to identify the range of the code, and add
   "RspRestored" labels to identify %rsp changes.
 * Extend the test to check this.

